name: Query
extra-info:
SELECT CASE
           WHEN
                  (SELECT count(*)
                   FROM 'store_sales.parquet' AS store_sales
                   WHERE ss_quantity BETWEEN 1 AND 20) > 74129 THEN
                  (SELECT avg(ss_ext_discount_amt)
                   FROM 'store_sales.parquet' AS store_sales
                   WHERE ss_quantity BETWEEN 1 AND 20)
           ELSE
                  (SELECT avg(ss_net_paid)
                   FROM 'store_sales.parquet' AS store_sales
                   WHERE ss_quantity BETWEEN 1 AND 20)
       END bucket1,
       CASE
           WHEN
                  (SELECT count(*)
                   FROM 'store_sales.parquet' AS store_sales
                   WHERE ss_quantity BETWEEN 21 AND 40) > 122840 THEN
                  (SELECT avg(ss_ext_discount_amt)
                   FROM 'store_sales.parquet' AS store_sales
                   WHERE ss_quantity BETWEEN 21 AND 40)
           ELSE
                  (SELECT avg(ss_net_paid)
                   FROM 'store_sales.parquet' AS store_sales
                   WHERE ss_quantity BETWEEN 21 AND 40)
       END bucket2,
       CASE
           WHEN
                  (SELECT count(*)
                   FROM 'store_sales.parquet' AS store_sales
                   WHERE ss_quantity BETWEEN 41 AND 60) > 56580 THEN
                  (SELECT avg(ss_ext_discount_amt)
                   FROM 'store_sales.parquet' AS store_sales
                   WHERE ss_quantity BETWEEN 41 AND 60)
           ELSE
                  (SELECT avg(ss_net_paid)
                   FROM 'store_sales.parquet' AS store_sales
                   WHERE ss_quantity BETWEEN 41 AND 60)
       END bucket3,
       CASE
           WHEN
                  (SELECT count(*)
                   FROM 'store_sales.parquet' AS store_sales
                   WHERE ss_quantity BETWEEN 61 AND 80) > 10097 THEN
                  (SELECT avg(ss_ext_discount_amt)
                   FROM 'store_sales.parquet' AS store_sales
                   WHERE ss_quantity BETWEEN 61 AND 80)
           ELSE
                  (SELECT avg(ss_net_paid)
                   FROM 'store_sales.parquet' AS store_sales
                   WHERE ss_quantity BETWEEN 61 AND 80)
       END bucket4,
       CASE
           WHEN
                  (SELECT count(*)
                   FROM 'store_sales.parquet' AS store_sales
                   WHERE ss_quantity BETWEEN 81 AND 100) > 165306 THEN
                  (SELECT avg(ss_ext_discount_amt)
                   FROM 'store_sales.parquet' AS store_sales
                   WHERE ss_quantity BETWEEN 81 AND 100)
           ELSE
                  (SELECT avg(ss_net_paid)
                   FROM 'store_sales.parquet' AS store_sales
                   WHERE ss_quantity BETWEEN 81 AND 100)
       END bucket5
FROM 'reason.parquet' AS reason
WHERE r_reason_sk = 1
